name: Chiroform Millenium Portable Table
descr:
Light 3-section portable table in high quality.

Features: height adjustable headpiece, armrest in front, armrest in both sides, height adjustable legs, extra nosehole, adjustable leg section.

Specifications: Dimension: 195x70 cm, Adjustable Height 64-90 cm, Weight 18 kg and max. loading 250 kg.

Standard colours: black and blue.
